## Docusaurus Sidebar Templates

### Fully autogenerated sidebar (sidebars.ts)
```ts
import type { SidebarsConfig } from '@docusaurus/plugin-content-docs';

const sidebars: SidebarsConfig = {
  docs: [{ type: 'autogenerated', dirName: '.' }]
};

export default sidebars;
```

### Manual top-level ordering with autogenerated categories (sidebars.ts)
```ts
import type { SidebarsConfig } from '@docusaurus/plugin-content-docs';

const sidebars: SidebarsConfig = {
  docs: [
    { type: 'autogenerated', dirName: 'getting-started' },
    { type: 'autogenerated', dirName: 'guides' },
    { type: 'autogenerated', dirName: 'reference' }
  ]
};

export default sidebars;
```

### Category that links to a doc (`docs/<folder>/_category_.json`)
```json
{
  "label": "Guides",
  "position": 2,
  "collapsed": true,
  "link": { "type": "doc", "id": "guides/overview" }
}
```

Place the doc at `docs/guides/overview.md` (same folder) so it is deduplicated from the item list and only available via the category link.

### Category with a generated index (no category doc yet)
```json
{
  "label": "Guides",
  "position": 2,
  "collapsed": true,
  "link": {
    "type": "generated-index",
    "title": "Guides",
    "description": "Browse all guides by topic.",
    "slug": "/guides"
  }
}
```

